{
  "stem": "27509.1",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So the-- the people, especially peasants from the entire locality around knew that address and came-- came to us directly to buy their sweaters whenever they could afford one, and that wasn't too often.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "What were the sleeping arrangements?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The sleeping arrangements were-- well, Father and Mother had the bedroom to themselves.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But part of the other space in their room was taken up with-- with bundles of yarn because there was no room to-- in the-- in the olden days, you didn't get yarn on spools.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You got them only in hanks even-- even if you used it for industrial purposes.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We ourselves had to rewind from the hanks onto spools, and we had in that big room, the first one that I have described, had 12 spindle winding machine.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Big, very big thing considering it was a private home, which did just that.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Spindles and we pushed on the hanks on it, and then put on a-- a-- a [? electrical ?] in moving spools to take the yarn down from the hanks because you couldn't put them on to machine from-- from the hanks.",
      "word_count": 42
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It had to go on the spools to have an even flow of yarn for the manufacture.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Excuse me.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Then the other rooms were also to such another degree shared between the-- the quarters of-- there was another bedroom where there were three beds.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But there was still room in the corner, and with the first overlocker arrived, and that was a major addition to the family and to the business because it changed manufacturing extraordinarily, because until the overlocker became available, the entire process of sewing up was done by hand.",
      "word_count": 48
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And people used to come and take out outdoor work.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
